item.dc:creator: @dillingo dillingo
item.description:
@dillingo wrote:

Is there a difference between delta and other sources? To change the initial starting point open player.java and search for the coordinates you start at now, and change them.

To change the tele to home open your client.java and search “home” then change the coordinates.
